<FIRST>r a BC-Quotes     06-03 0185</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Quotes,0189</SECOND>
<HEAD>Current Quotations</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   ``We are running very aggressively and proposing clear
solutions. ... A lot of people with other political concepts have
not seen such a thing before, and they are scared.'' _ Solidarity
leader Lech Walesa, commenting on Poland's parliamentary elections,
seen as the freest elections in Eastern Europe in 40 years.
</TEXT>
